snippet.title: A mixture SuperMario Odyssey, Celeste and Banjo Kazooie: Wishlist MOJITO Woody's Rescue now on Steam
snippet.description: Mojito Woody's Rescue is a cute 3D platformer adventure inspired by Super Mario Odyssey & Banjo Kazooie & Celeste. Play as Mojito and find your best dog friend Woody
